title: ODLO.City-Biathlon.07-08-2011.Puttlingen.ZDF.WEBRip.240p.XviD
description:
Since 2008 ODLO City Biathlon is an international summer biathlon event, held annually since 2005 in P?ttlingen in Saarland. In addition to active competitions for men and women, each consisting of one qualifying race and finals, it was in 2007, also a former All-Star race biathlon stars like Raphael Poir?e, Liv Grete Poir?e, Sven Fischer and Ricco Gross.


Participants 2011

Men: Ole Einar Bjoerndalen (NOR), Tarjei Boe (NOR), Michael Greis (GER), Martin Fourcade (FRA), Bjoern Ferry (SWE), Ivan Tcherezov (RUS), Andreas Birnbacher (GER), Daniel Boehm (GER)

Women: Kaisa Makarainen (FIN), Magdalena Neuner (GER), Andrea Henkel (GER), Helena Ekholm (SWE) will be replaced by Selina Gasparin (SUI), Tora Berger (NOR), Marie Laure Brunet (FRA), Darya Domracheva (BLR), Sabrina Buchholz (GER)
